%% Diagram: Multipart upload sequence
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant S as Storage Service

    C->>S: InitiateMultipartUpload(bucket, key)
    S-->>C: UploadId

    par Upload parts in parallel
        C->>S: UploadPart(UploadId, PartNumber=1, bytes)
        S-->>C: ETag_1
    and
        C->>S: UploadPart(UploadId, PartNumber=2, bytes)
        S-->>C: ETag_2
    and
        C->>S: UploadPart(UploadId, PartNumber=N, bytes)
        S-->>C: ETag_N
    end

    C->>S: CompleteMultipartUpload(UploadId, [ETag_1..ETag_N])
    S-->>C: 200 OK + final composite ETag

    Note over C,S: Lifecycle rule AbortIncompleteMultipartUpload<br/>cleans up abandoned uploads
